{"tid":1791280,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"2019年 【捉鬼論】重上熱門","createTime":"2019-12-20T16:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T17:11:46.000Z","uid":7971,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ded7822ad05f1d477bdbc79467acaa025c3ba758","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"(有片)正式宣佈 全面搜身搜袋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1791212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1791212</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n經歷完 2014，唔夠一個月嘅Poly<br />\n依家有人提議 全民學生捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n姐係之後所有前線手足互相猜疑？ <br />\n係未以後嘅運動和你捉？<br />\n日日開始時 互相猜疑 互相懷疑？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咩人最想你互相猜疑？</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係對家啊 <br />\n因為 內部分化 先會係最容易搞散場運動</span></span></strong><br />\n點解去到2019年今日<br />\n一個捉鬼論post 仲可以有接近200人正評？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">就算無上過前面踢波 踢前鋒位<br />\n都諗下 如果你踢波個陣 互相猜疑會點啦</span><br />\n<br />\n前線唔撚係condom啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係手足啊 ！！！"},{"pid":"d041e6ae425ef64624d0e9a87e4c2c979a8825c2","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"個個post嘅樓主<br />\n如果之後有人因為你嘅post 然後玩捉鬼<br />\n之後因爲咁對場運動有咩影響 令手足捉鬼捉出事 <br />\n(例如poly之戰前個兩日)<br />\n你良心過唔過意得去啊！"},{"pid":"d554e0476e2c9333552f764f4f7ba5ca74e5e53c","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:15:00.000Z","msg":"怎樣在香港成為勇武：<br />\n<br />\n1）要時刻保持冷靜，不可對市民動氣<br />\n2）要巧妙避過黑警追捕<br />\n3）面對黑警，要懂得還擊，但不可有嚴重傷害<br />\n4）不可TK<br />\n5）不可大隻<br />\n6）不可用3m 60926等濾罐，因為是pink team，是鬼<br />\n7）不可破壞狗鐵，因為「多謝黑警」<br />\n8）要聽從和理非指示，支持和理非<br />\n9）示威後，要保護和理非走<br />\n10）要幫手重建連儂牆<br />\n11) 仲讀緊書，要係學生<br />\n12）和理非要求休息時務必休息，要求出動時立即出動<br />\n13）不可指責和理非，否則立即割蓆<br />\n14）可以裝修紅店黑店，但需準確預計火種燃燒速度、方向、角度，不可波及其他建築<br />\n15）懂光合作用，可辭職全身投入抗爭<br />\n16）不可中計<br />\n17）不可衝動<br />\n18）可以嗌黑警死全家，但不可真實傷害黑警家人<br />\n19）擁有隨意門，在黑警圍困及包圍下需想辦法逃出理大投票，或自首<br />\n20）面對親中暴徒持刀攻擊時，不可還手，需巧妙避開<br />\n21）不可自衛<br />\n22）不可淆底<br />\n23）撤退時需1212慢慢行，隻閪手不可小兒痲瘅"},{"pid":"21c3f1b0f04b48cce97bc2204b9177aeea9044b4","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"點解仲有人會支持佢！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18be078a72ff56365f03b22082b59e72204e5567","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2f574435787c4079101f4db3f9a1b7ec52cc9c6c","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd0fa2c574133b58ea7ee12798a176cab470409f","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:16:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"85e2e0c3d2fca1aba0371fce354bfc35c0847c12","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4072ffbc2cb8990d4af1fc960b59ebc4e491864b","tid":1791280,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e4e426908474ce6ad184a3f8090f01d4b28332e8","tid":1791280,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"推 唔捉鬼 夠人多佢哋做唔到野"},{"pid":"83132c1d41994e29d49ece56070703024da536ff","tid":1791280,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12.22  愛丁堡<br />\n12.21  721五個月 <br />\n12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.24  夜晚尖咀見<br />\n12.31  和你拖<br />\n20